{"tid":354442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九寨溝風景區連諾日朗瀑布都GG","createTime":"2017-08-10T12:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T13:13:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b44077fd7ca9ddcc65d0fb5bff3ce14fbe89b93b","tid":354442,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170810/large/1502367048_4d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170810%2Flarge%2F1502367048_4d0a.jpg&h=a7a4686f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 四川九寨溝前晚發生7級地震後，今天再失一處美景！九寨溝著名景區諾日朗瀑布今日下午3時40分突然坍塌，原本涓涓的細流變成急湍的流水，瀑布下的清湖，也變成了泥潭。<br />\n<br />\n據在現場的內地媒體記者指，她們先聽到一聲山崩巨響，到山下後，她們來到諾日朗瀑布前面，發現該瀑布已變了一副模樣。據一名當地民兵稱，他經過時碰巧遇到諾日朗瀑布坍塌，原本涓涓細流，變成了一股非常湍急的急流，瀑布下方的清澈湖水，也變成了泥潭。<br />\n<br />\n諾日朗瀑布位處海拔2,365米，瀑寬270米，落差20米，寬達300米，是中國大型鈣華瀑布之一，也是中國最寬的瀑布。藏語中，諾日朗是偉岸高大的意思，因此，諾日朗瀑布意思就是雄偉壯觀的瀑布。央視1986年版電視劇《西遊記》的片尾，也在此拍攝。"},{"pid":"3fe8af8fa48b3bfed4add16f917c48f3bac5cf2a","tid":354442,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"原本涓涓細流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張相上個月影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/210943_d86eea96aa4f476506b6c9d3dd362010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F210943_d86eea96aa4f476506b6c9d3dd362010.jpg&h=88c0788b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁都可以作新聞"},{"pid":"06934e610305e2812fb6c460ce492534e2876281","tid":354442,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原本涓涓細流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張相上個月影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/210943_d86eea96aa4f476506b6c9d3dd362010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F210943_d86eea96aa4f476506b6c9d3dd362010.jpg&h=88c0788b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁都可以作新聞</blockquote><br />\n變成一堆泥潭屎水就已經夠曬可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}